desc.en: Fantastical Hohhot commuter rail network, including six national rail lines and one private rail line. Interchanges with the metro are possible. Stations have been added to the real-life railway lines and all of them are open for passenger services.
desc.zh-Hans: 幻想的呼和浩特通勤铁路网络，包括6条国铁线路和一条私铁线路。可与地铁换乘。在现实中的铁路线基础上增加了车站，并全部开通客运服务。
